# Local secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in.
# `npm run cf-typegen` picks up the keys here/in .dev.vars and adds them to the
# typed `Env`. In production set this with: `wrangler secret put GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY`.

# Google AI Studio (Gemini) API key. Backend-only secret — never expose to the
# frontend, never commit the real value, never use a VITE_* variable for this.
GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY="your-google-ai-studio-key"
